name: PRULIA Member Feedback Report
query:
SELECT
 `tabPRULIA Feedback`.`member` as "PRULIA ID:Data/PRULIA ID:80",
 `tabPRULIA Feedback`.`member_name` as "Sender Name:Data/Sender Name:80",
 `tabPRULIA Feedback`.`submission_date` as "Submission Date:Date/Submission Date:80",
 `tabPRULIA Feedback`.`remark` as "Feedback Remark:Date/Feedback Remark:200",
 `tabPRULIA Feedback`.`category` as "Feedback Category:Link/Feedback Category:80"
 FROM
  `abPRULIA Feedback`
